Amplify Visual Impact In Waterfall Charts with Conditional Formatting
Help users quickly spot areas of interest and get deeper exploration of their data by adding conditional formatting to waterfall charts.

Where: This change applies to CRM Analytics in Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic.
How: Open or create a dashboard with a waterfall chart, click Formatting and open Conditional Formatting, apply a rule and click Done.
